query:
SELECT productId, partNumber, name, description 
FROM products 
WHERE brand = 'Agilent' 
AND (
  partNumber IN ('820950-902', '821125-902', '821250-902', '820975-902', '821150-902')
  OR productId IN ('AGIL-820950-902', 'AGIL-821125-902', 'AGIL-821250-902', 'AGIL-820975-902', 'AGIL-821150-902')
)
LIMIT 10
